<file path="templates/sections/faq.html">
<section class="faq-section" id="faq">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Get answers to common questions about our property services</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-container">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question flex items-center justify-between" aria-expanded="false">
                    <span>How quickly can you visit my property?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>We typically schedule property visits within 24-48 hours of your request. For urgent situations or emergencies, we offer same-day service (additional fees may apply). Simply call or WhatsApp us, and we'll coordinate a visit that works with your schedule.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question flex items-center justify-between" aria-expanded="false">
                    <span>What areas of Puerto Rico do you serve?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>We primarily serve the San Juan metropolitan area, including Carolina, Dorado, Bayam√≥n, and surrounding municipalities. For properties in other parts of Puerto Rico, please contact us to discuss availability and any additional travel fees that may apply.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question flex items-center justify-between" aria-expanded="false">
                    <span>How do I receive reports after property visits?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>After each visit, you'll receive a detailed report via your preferred method - WhatsApp, email, or both. Reports include high-quality photos, videos when relevant, and detailed notes about your property's condition. You'll receive these within 24 hours of our visit, often same-day.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question flex items-center justify-between" aria-expanded="false">
                    <span>Do you offer emergency services?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Yes! If you need an urgent property check (water leaks, storm damage, security concerns), we offer same-day emergency visits. Call or WhatsApp us immediately, and we'll prioritize your property. Emergency services are available 7 days a week.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question flex items-center justify-between" aria-expanded="false">
                    <span>Can I cancel my service anytime?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Absolutely! We don't require long-term contracts. You pay only for the services you need, when you need them. Monthly package clients can cancel with 30 days notice. Our goal is to earn your trust through great service, not trap you in contracts.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question flex items-center justify-between" aria-expanded="false">
                    <span>How do I pay for services?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>We accept credit cards, debit cards, PayPal, Venmo, Zelle, and bank transfers. For one-time services, payment is due before the visit. Monthly package clients are billed at the beginning of each month. All transactions are secure and you'll receive detailed invoices.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question flex items-center justify-between" aria-expanded="false">
                    <span>What if you find a problem during a visit?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>We'll notify you immediately via phone or WhatsApp with photos/videos of any issues found. Depending on the situation, we can coordinate with local contractors, arrange emergency repairs, or simply document the issue for your review. You always have final say on what actions to take.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question flex items-center justify-between" aria-expanded="false">
                    <span>Are you insured and licensed?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Yes! We carry full liability insurance and are properly licensed to operate in Puerto Rico. We can provide proof of insurance upon request. Your property and belongings are protected during our visits.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
</file>

